Package wackpackr.core

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Compressor  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HuffCompressor
    Compression and decompression with a simplistic implementation of the Huffman algorithm.
    HuffTreeParser
    Helper class that handles forming and parsing of frequency-sorted prefix trees needed in Huffman compression and decompression.
    LZSSCompressor
    Compression and decompression with a simplistic implementation of the LZSS algorithm.
    LZSSWindowOperator
    Helper class that handles the "sliding window" dictionary needed in LZSS compression and decompression.
    LZWCompressor
    Compression and decompression with a simplistic implementation of the LZW algorithm.
    LZWDictionary
    Helper class that handles the dictionary needed in LZW compression and decompression.
